subject: Attn: Beneficiary,
body:
Attn: Beneficiary,
I sent the ATM card package to your address do you received it if not reconfirm below information again to me
Postal address;
Full Names:
Direct telephone number;

Mr.John Joe
Chief Executive Officer of ATM card
Africa Nigeria

subject: Re:   Attn: Beneficiary,
body:
Hello Joe,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm afraid I haven't received any ATM card package at my address. Could you please provide more details about this package? What does it contain and why was it sent to me?

Looking forward to hearing from you.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Alice
